{
  "stem": "27150.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, and we in a flat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a three-room flat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got the servant's flat, which was sort of 6-foot wide, you see, and 6 foot-- 8 foot long, you see.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the bed and room to pass through, and just hanging this-- and it was the servant room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was a Russian woman, you see, with a little boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then was a couple with the little boy in one room, and another couple in the second room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we looked what we're going to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you see, we started traveling second class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because there were two classes, first and second class on the trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And eventually, you see, people were running out of money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they didn't want to go to Hongkew to those warehouses and three-story beds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You see, and with the help of the Jews, now the Jewish club got a lease of the American club.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, which was beautifully equipped you see, with 10-pin bowling, and also they were not automatic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because the Chinese were standing and putting back the things-- and-- the pins.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the old club, they gave the grand floor to the Shiva.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The first floor for living quarters for the Shiva [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the second floor, there was a few rooms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they put up curtains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in every room were three couples, and in one room was 10 bunch of boys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was very nice, just very lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At the end of the corridor was a window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I rustled up a couple of sheets of [NON-ENGLISH], you know, and I made myself a room from the end of the corridor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- that was you see that everything stops, all sort of business stops.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
